Usage: display_timing_map [-help] [-step <float>] [-threshold <float>] { -check_type {setup hold} | -clear }

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-check_type {setup hold}     # Specifies the check_type. (enum, required)
-clear                       # clear the timingMap (bool, optional)
-step <float>                # Specifies the step. (float, optional)
-threshold <float>           # Specifies the slack threshold (float, optional)